              We connect Turkish companies with global markets through prestigious fairs organized worldwide.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Sector Filter -->
          <div class="mb-8">
            <!-- Desktop Filter -->
            <div class="hidden md:flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
